✅ Features

📌 Task Management: Add, mark complete, and delete tasks effortlessly.

📅 Date & Time Picker: Select specific dates and times using an interactive calendar.

🔵 Dynamic UI Effects: Clicking the calendar icon highlights the placeholder in blue and opens a custom datetime picker.

🎨 Modern UI: Features a sleek, dark purple-blue gradient background with a glassmorphism card effect.

🌗 Toggle Theme: Seamlessly switch between light and dark modes.

📤 Export Tasks: Export your to-do list in one click.

📱 Responsive Design: Optimized for both mobile and desktop devices.



---

💻 Tech Stack

HTML5 – Structure and layout

CSS3 – Styling with gradients, glass effects, and animations

JavaScript (Vanilla) – Core functionality and user interaction
